===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*pleh₂-}}
1560s. From {{compound|en|Pole|land}}, from {{etyl|de|en}} {{m|de|Pole}}, singular of {{m|de|Polen}}, from {{etyl|pl|en}} {{m|pl|Polanie||Poles|lit=field dwellers}}, from {{etyl|sla-pro|en}} {{m|sla-pro|*poľane}}, plural of {{m|sla-pro|*poľaninъ||field dweller}}, from {{m|sla-pro|*poľe||field}} + {{m|sla-pro|*-ěninъ}}, ultimately from {{der|sla-pro|ine-pro|*pleh₂-|t=flat, wide}}.

